# PyAnimator
Make a cool and awesome animation with one line of code !

# Usage

```
import PyAnimator
                      MESSAGE               Colors TIME X  Y  INFINITE  DOTS ON THE END
PyAnimator.animation("Hi !, i am PyAnimator!", 10, 0.5, 0, 0, inf=True, dots=True)
```


